java_cup.runtime
Class Symbol

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--java_cup.runtime.Symbol
public class Symbol
extends Object

Defines the Symbol class, which is used to represent all terminals and nonterminals while parsing. The lexer should pass CUP Symbols and CUP returns a Symbol.
